thread.title: BRIEF-Eften Real Estate Fund Iii Consolidated Sales Revenue For Year 2017 Up At EUR 7.3 Million

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Eften Real Estate Fund Iii Consolidated Sales Revenue For Year 2017 Up At EUR 7.3 Million
text:
Feb 28 (Reuters) - Eften Real Estate Fund Iii As:
* SAYS CONSOLIDATED SALES REVENUE FOR YEAR 2017 WAS EUR 7.3 MILLION, WHICH INCREASED BY 37% IN A YEAR‍​
* SAYS 2017 THE GROUP‘S EBITDA TOTALLED EUR 5.7 MILLION (2016: EUR 4.0 MILLION)
* SAYS 2017 NET PROFIT AMOUNTED TO EUR 6.6 MILLION, INCREASING BY 51% COMPARED TO 2016 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Gdynia Newsroom)
